literal "false"

\end_inset

.
 Furthermore,
 disturbance at haulouts can cause stampedes,
 resulting in mass calf and juvenile mortality.
 Continued sea ice decline and a concomitant increase in the intensity and expansion of industrial and shipping activities in Pacific Arctic waters 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "silber_vessel_2019"
literal "false"

\end_inset

